OL,3,CGolf club discovers hidden Victorian
OL,4,Cwine cellar beneath 13th hole
OL,6,FA golf club has uncovered a
OL,7,F"incredible" piece of history after a
OL,8,Fsinkhole on the course revealed a
OL,9,Fhidden Victorian wine cellar.
OL,11,FGroundskeepers at Davyhulme Park Golf
OL,12,FClub, in Urmston, Manchester, were
OL,13,Finvestigating a dip in the turf on the
OL,14,F13th hole when they discovered a brick
OL,15,Fchamber dating back more than a
OL,16,Fcentury.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
