OL,3,CGolf club discovers hidden Victorian
OL,4,Cwine cellar beneath 13th hole
OL,6,FInside the vault, the team found
OL,7,Fdozens of historic wine and port
OL,8,Fbottles, believed to date back to the
OL,9,Foriginal Davyhulme Hall which was
OL,10,Fdemolished in 1888.
OL,12,FThe grand manor house stood on the
OL,13,Fland long before it was converted into
OL,14,Fa golf course in 1911.
OL,16,FThe Trafford club revealed their
OL,17,Fdiscovery on social media with a video
OL,18,Fshowing the underground cellar. A
OL,19,Fspokesperson said: "An exciting
OL,20,Fdiscovery on the course today!
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
