PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1772572327
OL,3,CGolf club discovers hidden Victorian
OL,4,Cwine cellar beneath 13th hole
OL,6,F"Following the appearance of a
OL,7,Fsinkhole on the 13th hole, our greens
OL,8,Fteam uncovered what appears to be an
OL,9,Fold cellar, believed to date back to
OL,10,Fthe original manor house.
OL,12,F"Over 100 years old and filled with
OL,13,Fhistoric wine and port bottles - what
OL,14,Fan incredible piece of our club's
OL,15,Fhistory!"
OL,17,FSite managers say the area around the
OL,18,F13th hole remains cordoned off while
OL,19,Fstructural engineers and historians
OL,20,Ffrom the local council assess the site.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
